<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as we race at Usui Pass,</b></font>

155
00:10:15,054 --> 00:10:18,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we have to win, no matter who we race.</b></font>

156
00:10:18,794 --> 00:10:22,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't accept anything less.</b></font>

157
00:10:22,864 --> 00:10:25,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

158
00:10:25,004 --> 00:10:28,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have to win, no matter what.</b></font>

159
00:10:28,474 --> 00:10:31,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if it's against the Eight-Six.</b></font>

160
00:10:31,044 --> 00:10:34,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Absolutely.</b></font>

161
00:10:38,744 --> 00:10:43,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, there's no use racing if you're not into it.</b></font>

162
00:10:43,414 --> 00:10:46,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani and I will let them know.</b></font>

163
00:10:46,654 --> 00:10:49,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys turn around here.</b></font>

164
00:10:50,924 --> 00:10:53,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I'm sorry, Takumi.</b></font>

165
00:10:53,894 --> 00:10:57,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He means it, Takumi.</b></font>

166
00:10:57,164 --> 00:11:01,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenji, I'm not going back.</b></font>

167
00:11:01,504 --> 00:11:03,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

168
00:11:03,534 --> 00:11:06,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going because...</b></font>

169
00:11:06,044 --> 00:11:08,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I do want to race her.</b></font>

170
00:11:08,374 --> 00:11:11,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not going back.</b></font>

171
00:11:11,584 --> 00:11:13,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

172
00:11:14,584 --> 00:11:19,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But Takumi, you saw what Mako is capable of.</b></font>

173
00:11:19,254 --> 00:11:22,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's too much for you.</b></font>

174
00:11:22,394 --> 00:11:26,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Even you can't beat her.
--I know.</b></font>

175
00:11:26,424 --> 00:11:29,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't about winning or losing.</b></font>

176
00:11:29,394 --> 00:11:31,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't say that!</b></font>

177
00:11:31,404 --> 00:11:35,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six of Mount Akina is famous now!</b></font>

178
00:11:35,074 --> 00:11:36,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have some pride.</b></font>

179
00:11:36,804 --> 00:11:40,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not good at that sort of thing.</b></font>

180
00:11:40,204 --> 00:11:42,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I happened to win some local races,</b></font>

181
00:11:42,974 --> 00:11:47,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the rumors exaggerated my abilities.</b></font>

182
00:11:48,484 --> 00:11:52,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would feel better if
rumors like that went away.</b></font>

183
00:11:52,154 --> 00:11:54,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey...
--Come on!</b></font>

184
00:11:54,624 --> 00:11:56,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going.</b></font>

185
00:11:56,824 --> 00:12:02,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want to attack this
new pass as well as I can.</b></font>

186
00:12:06,134 --> 00:12:10,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I should apologize for my harsh words earlier.</b></font>

187
00:12:10,234 --> 00:12:14,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could we say anything
to him after that, really?</b></font>

188
00:12:14,314 --> 00:12:16,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

189
00:12:16,174 --> 00:12:20,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, he's one of a kind for sure.</b></font>

190
00:12:20,414 --> 00:12:23,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's strange.</b></font>

191
00:12:23,654 --> 00:12:26,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's hard to tell if he's special...</b></font>

192
00:12:26,924 --> 00:12:29,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...or simply "off."</b></font>

193
00:12:43,674 --> 00:12:45,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The tires look good.</b></font>

194
00:12:45,804 --> 00:12:49,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The pressure is ideal for this road.</b></font>

195
00:12:49,644 --> 00:12:53,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think it's necessary
to make any more adjustments.</b></font>

196
00:12:53,484 --> 00:12:55,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you say so, Sayuki.</b></font>

197
00:12:55,954 --> 00:12:57,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you know,</b></font>

198
00:12:57,724 --> 00:13:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but in this kind of race,
avoid wide-angle drifts.</b></font>

199
00:13:02,154 --> 00:13:06,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it's crucial to know when
to drift and when not to drift,</b></font>

200
00:13:06,994 --> 00:13:11,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>especially with Usui's continuous turns.</b></font>

201
00:13:11,164 --> 00:13:15,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm with you, so believe in
your technique and go for it.</b></font>

202
00:13:15,334 --> 00:13:17,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You won't lose to anyone!</b></font>

203
00:13:20,204 --> 00:13:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't let you down.</b></font>

204
00:13:22,674 --> 00:13:25,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Together, we're one winning team.</b></font>

205
00:13:25,184 --> 00:13:28,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--I'm fired up, Sayuki!</b></font>

206
00:13:28,214 --> 00:13:31,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never felt this good before.</b></font>

207
00:13:31,154 --> 00:13:34,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm excited to see how the race will turn out...</i></b></font>

208
00:13:34,824 --> 00:13:37,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and how good he really is.</i></b></font>

209
00:13:58,744 --> 00:14:01,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, how are you gonna win this race, Takumi?</b></font>

210
00:14:01,754 --> 00:14:04,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you have a plan? Tell me!</b></font>

211
00:14:04,424 --> 00:14:06,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not really.</b></font>

212
00:14:06,124 --> 00:14:07,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

213
00:14:07,694 --> 00:14:09,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't you think of something?</b></font>

214
00:14:09,524 --> 00:14:12,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I refuse to see you lose.</b></font>

215
00:14:23,034 --> 00:14:24,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about this?</b></font>

216
00:14:24,704 --> 00:14:28,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Usui Pass is narrow
and has no straight lines...</b></font>

217
00:14:28,374 --> 00:14:32,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so jump the gun and get ahead!</b></font>

218
00:14:32,644 --> 00:14:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the...?</b></font>

219
00:14:33,884 --> 00:14:39,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And you can block her the rest
of the way to the finish line!</b></font>

220
00:14:39,054 --> 00:14:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't do that, 'cuz it's unfair.</b></font>

221
00:14:43,054 --> 00:14:47,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if she gets ahead of you, it's over.</b></font>

222
00:14:47,224 --> 00:14:49,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's true...</b></font>

223
00:14:52,564 --> 00:14:56,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, we need to come up with a plan!</b></font>

224
00:14:56,174 --> 00:14:59,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Her car has four wheels just like yours...</b></font>

225
00:15:11,124 --> 00:15:13,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

226
00:15:14,324 --> 00:15:19,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you really the driver of
the Eight-Six of Mount Akina?</b></font>

227
00:15:19,194 --> 00:15:21,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable.</b></font>

228
00:15:21,164 --> 00:15:22,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How old are you, anyway?</b></font>

229
00:15:22,934 --> 00:15:24,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm eighteen.</b></font>

230
00:15:24,934 --> 00:15:29,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eighteen? A high school kid?
You've gotta be kidding me...</b></font>

231
00:15:29,104 --> 00:15:32,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Twenty isn't much older than eighteen.</b></font>

232
00:15:32,104 --> 00:15:33,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And they're girls.</b></font>

233
00:15:33,844 --> 00:15:39,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now we really can't lose to him, right, Mako?</b></font>

234
00:15:50,724 --> 00:15:53,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's talk about the race.</b></font>

235
00:15:57,734 --> 00:16:00,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think it's a good idea
to start side by side here,</b></font>

236
00:16:00,904 --> 00:16:03,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because whoever has a better start</b></font>

237
00:16:03,404 --> 00:16:07,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has a definite advantage.</b></font>

238
00:16:07,244 --> 00:16:11,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd hate to argue over who
cheated and jumped the gun.</b></font>

239
00:16:11,314 --> 00:16:12,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There goes my plan!</b></font>

240
00:16:12,914 --> 00:16:15,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then how?</b></font>

241
00:16:15,084 --> 00:16:18,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about a "cat and mouse" race?</b></font>

242
00:16:18,224 --> 00:16:20,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a chase race.</b></font>

243
00:16:20,424 --> 00:16:22,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the mouse gets away, it's over.</b></font>

244
00:16:22,924 --> 00:16:27,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If not, we keep switching
positions until someone wins.</b></font>

245
00:16:27,594 --> 00:16:29,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a "sudden-death death match."</b></font>

246
00:16:29,934 --> 00:16:33,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Well?
--That's fine.</b></font>

247
00:16:33,004 --> 00:16:34,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since we're the locals here,</b></font>

248
00:16:34,774 --> 00:16:40,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you get to choose whether you
want to be the cat or the mouse.</b></font>

249
00:16:41,214 --> 00:16:43,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Well...
--Hold on a sec!</b></font>

250
00:16:43,444 --> 00:16:45,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come here, Takumi.</b></font>

251
00:16:47,584 --> 00:16:51,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With this rule, you should go in front first.</b></font>

252
00:16:51,754 --> 00:16:54,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It won't end with one race,</b></font>

253
00:16:54,084 --> 00:16:56,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but at least you get one practice.</b></font>

254
00:16:56,254 --> 00:16:59,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's better to lose in the second race.</b></font>

255
00:16:59,194 --> 00:17:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll go in front first.</b></font>

256
00:17:02,394 --> 00:17:05,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll win in the second race, then.</b></font>

257
00:17:05,304 --> 00:17:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mean to ignore your good advice,</b></font>

258
00:17:10,474 --> 00:17:14,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't think I like that.</b></font>

259
00:17:14,144 --> 00:17:16,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you saying, Takumi?!</b></font>

260
00:17:16,944 --> 00:17:19,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I'll chase her first.
--What?!</b></font>

261
00:17:19,884 --> 00:17:23,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Wha...?!
--Think it over, Takumi!</b></font>

262
00:17:23,454 --> 00:17:26,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is my race, so let me decide.</b></font>

263
00:17:26,454 --> 00:17:28,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...!</b></font>

264
00:17:30,794 --> 00:17:33,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I'll chase.
--What?</b></font>

265
00:17:33,564 --> 00:17:36,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll chase?</b></font>

266
00:17:36,164 --> 00:17:39,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is he trying to insult us, or is he an idiot?</b></font>

267
00:17:40,564 --> 00:17:42,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's okay. I'll smoke him!</b></font>

268
00:17:57,254 --> 00:18:00,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is it? I'm busy.</b></font>

269
00:18:02,294 --> 00:18:04,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

270
00:18:04,594 --> 00:18:06,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Bunta?</b></font>

271
00:18:06,094 --> 00:18:07,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's only you.</b></font>

272
00:18:07,934 --> 00:18:10,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm busy right now.</b></font>

273
00:18:10,194 --> 00:18:14,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I should tell you
something about Takumi...</b></font>

274
00:18:16,274 --> 00:18:18,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Should we start the race?</b></font>

275
00:18:18,874 --> 00:18:22,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He went to Usui for a race? So?</b></font>

276
00:18:22,274 --> 00:18:25,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"So?" Is that all you can say?</b></font>

277
00:18:25,944 --> 00:18:27,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't you worried?</b></font>

278
00:18:27,884 --> 00:18:31,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not really. He's my son, you know?</b></font>

279
00:18:31,124 --> 00:18:34,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll go slowly, so just follow us.</b></font>

280
00:18:34,854 --> 00:18:39,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After the first turn, we'll go full speed.</b></font>

281
00:18:39,164 --> 00:18:41,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the beginning of the race.</b></font>

282
00:19:01,584 --> 00:19:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that all you have to say?</b></font>

283
00:19:04,014 --> 00:19:05,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all.</b></font>

284
00:19:05,554 --> 00:19:09,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm busy, so don't call me about nonsense.</b></font>

285
00:19:10,054 --> 00:19:12,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Bunta?!</b></font>

286
00:19:15,934 --> 00:19:19,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was an idiot, Takumi.</b></font>

287
00:19:19,064 --> 00:19:21,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I realize that now.</b></font>

288
00:19:21,234 --> 00:19:23,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know...</b></font>

289
00:19:23,404 --> 00:19:28,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that the only reason you
agreed to try this losing race</b></font>

290
00:19:28,544 --> 00:19:30,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>was to save my ego.</b></font>

291
00:19:30,944 --> 00:19:34,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm regretting it now.</b></font>

292
00:19:34,614 --> 00:19:37,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're Akina's racer.</b></font>

293
00:19:37,784 --> 00:19:40,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're our pride.</b></font>

294
00:19:43,394 --> 00:19:46,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a huge mistake.</b></font>

295
00:19:47,594 --> 00:19:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't wanna see you lose
because of my stupidity.</b></font>

296
00:19:52,864 --> 00:19:55,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He won't lose, Iketani!</b></font>

297
00:19:55,274 --> 00:19:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Reality isn't that simple, you know.</b></font>

298
00:19:59,704 --> 00:20:01,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's my fault.</b></font>

299
00:20:01,144 --> 00:20:02,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani...</b></font>

300
00:20:04,144 --> 00:20:06,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani...</b></font>

301
00:20:06,084 --> 00:20:09,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I chose to be the cat for a reason.</b></font>

302
00:20:09,814 --> 00:20:11,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

303
00:20:13,624 --> 00:20:15,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not sure if I'll win,</b></font>

304
00:20:15,954 --> 00:20:19,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm not here to lose.</b></font>

305
00:20:19,824 --> 00:20:23,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, you do have a plan?</b></font>

306
00:20:23,494 --> 00:20:26,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not really a plan...</b></font>

307
00:20:26,434 --> 00:20:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More like an inspiration.</b></font>

308
00:20:28,834 --> 00:20:33,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What is it, Takumi?
--Tell us!</b></font>

309
00:20:33,304 --> 00:20:36,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how fast she is,</b></font>

310
00:20:36,174 --> 00:20:38,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>she can't fly.</b></font>

311
00:20:38,014 --> 00:20:39,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

312
00:20:39,684 --> 00:20:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's driving on four wheels, too.</b></font>

313
00:20:43,014 --> 00:20:44,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four wheels...?</b></font>

314
00:20:44,684 --> 00:20:47,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then I should be able to turn these corners</b></font>

315
00:20:47,684 --> 00:20:51,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as fast and as well as she can,</b></font>

316
00:20:51,694 --> 00:20:54,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>don't you think?</b></font>

317
00:20:54,324 --> 00:20:56,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right!</b></font>

318
00:20:56,864 --> 00:20:59,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Theoretically, it's true.</b></font>

319
00:20:59,534 --> 00:21:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's crazy talk!</b></font>

320
00:21:01,874 --> 00:21:03,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're going!</b></font>

321
00:21:09,174 --> 00:21:10,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, Mako!</b></font>

322
00:21:10,674 --> 00:21:12,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's finish him quickly!</b></font>

323
00:21:12,784 --> 00:21:17,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, Sayuki. I'll show you the best race ever!</b></font>

324
00:21:57,024 --> 00:21:58,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow!</b></font>

325
00:21:58,364 --> 00:22:00,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're going full throttle already!</b></font>

326
00:22:00,994 --> 00:22:05,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's first "away" race has finally started.</b></font>

327
00:22:05,604 --> 00:22:11,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi is at a serious
disadvantage in this race, though.</b></font>

328
00:22:11,374 --> 00:22:13,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not worried...</b></font>

329
00:22:13,574 --> 00:22:18,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...because I know he'll win!</b></font>

330
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was a time when I</i>
<i>wandered aimlessly, tired of love</i></b></font>

331
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost sight of myself and gave in to desire</i></b></font>

332
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But destiny is ever-changing</i></b></font>

333
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And charmed by innocent eyes</i></b></font>

334
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I hold you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

335
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All I can say is that I believe</i>
<i>my feelings are true</i></b></font>

336
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's enjoy our happiness...</i></b></font>

337
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Into our shining future</i></b></font>

338
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We'll prove countless times...</i></b></font>

339
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Our passion will last for eternity!</i></b></font>

340
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I embrace you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

341
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I lose everything that I have,</i>
<i>I will never let you go</i></b></font>

342
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom, my beautiful...</i></b></font>

343
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and miraculous flower</i></b></font>

344
00:24:26,244 --> 00:24:29,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mako, we can't lose on our own turf!</i></b></font>

345
00:24:29,544 --> 00:24:32,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--We're street racers!</i>
<i>--Yeah.</i></b></font>

346
00:24:32,684 --> 00:24:36,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What will you do if Mako quits racing, Sayuki?</i></b></font>

347
00:24:36,084 --> 00:24:38,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--I'll still be racing!</i>
<i>--Sayuki...</i></b></font>

348
00:24:38,584 --> 00:24:42,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--So, you won't retire?</i>
<i>--I'll be racing after men!</i></b></font>

349
00:24:42,654 --> 00:24:46,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--Huh?</i>
<i>--Where are all the good men?</i></b></font>

350
00:24:46,264 --> 00:24:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Where are they...?</i></b></font>

351
00:24:48,494 --> 00:24:49,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>See ya, Sayuki.</i></b></font>

352
00:24:49,864 --> 00:24:51,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D...</i></b></font>

353
00:24:51,264 --> 00:24:53,604
